ing: 1/3 cup vanilla-flavored or plain Greek yogurt
3 mandarin or clementine oranges - peeled, pith removed, sectioned
des: "For an on-the-go breakfast or after-school snack this orange and banana smoothie with chia seeds can't be beat."
ins: Place yogurt, oranges, banana, chia seeds and ice cubes in blender container. Cover and process until smooth.
